lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: Chirp? (Where are you from? I'm from the big tree in Cashew Homes!)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: Cheep... cheep? (You'll come by again, won't you?)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Cashew is hopping up and down. She looks happy to see you!)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Cashew makes a trilling noise. She's inviting you to sing a song with her!)

Cashew sprite random dialogue 5, when Qu.key: Cashew sprite random dialogue 5, when Quingee has a clothing item attached

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: Che-cheep! (I'm learning how to deliver mail!)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: Chireep? (How did I do? I hope you liked your delivery!)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Cashew is singing a small song. It's relaxing...)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Can you draw? I've been trying, but it's very difficult...)

Cashew sprite random dialogue 12, friend.key: Cashew sprite random dialogue 12, friendship with Wander

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: Chirp? Scree-ree... (Will you visit again? I think Wander likes seeing you around.)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Cashew looks cozy, nestled in Wander's backpack.)

lines.name: Cashew
lines.text: (Oh... Cashew seems to be taking a nap.)
